  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Towercore: Survivors is a challenging dark fantasy survival game with minimalistic gameplay and roguelite elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dark creatures are coming, and you are the only obstacle to stop them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover what is the origin of the monsters to find a way to stop them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive night by night in those monster-infested lands! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/8431309f8ff09991e188e1370185aa61.avif?t=1748947478\" width=320 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Discord server to get involved in the development of this game (Link in the sidebar).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect weapons and magical items <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/910b4a02552d0521f7277588decd1aa2.avif?t=1748947478\" width=580 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Level up to become more and more powerful!  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/ed21ff644ed904bc6a0af3462dcb31ca.avif?t=1748947478\" width=580 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 15 achievements <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/b6a3adf004091d7c5dc10fc0617fbeb4.avif?t=1748947478\" width=590 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 45 Collectibles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/9d94e039758dd6ba4a71523ea9e37757.avif?t=1748947478\" width=580 height=540 /></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Towercore: Survivors is a challenging dark fantasy survival game with minimalistic gameplay and roguelite elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dark creatures are coming, and you are the only obstacle to stop them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover what is the origin of the monsters to find a way to stop them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive night by night in those monster-infested lands! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/8431309f8ff09991e188e1370185aa61.avif?t=1748947478\" width=320 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Discord server to get involved in the development of this game (Link in the sidebar).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect weapons and magical items <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/910b4a02552d0521f7277588decd1aa2.avif?t=1748947478\" width=580 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Level up to become more and more powerful!  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/ed21ff644ed904bc6a0af3462dcb31ca.avif?t=1748947478\" width=580 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 15 achievements <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/b6a3adf004091d7c5dc10fc0617fbeb4.avif?t=1748947478\" width=590 height=540 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 45 Collectibles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2630210/extras/9d94e039758dd6ba4a71523ea9e37757.avif?t=1748947478\" width=580 height=540 /></span></p></li></ul>",
